  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To obtain evidence of content validity and reliability of the Colorado Adult Joint Assessment
      Scale (CAJAS), a clinician-reported outcome (ClinRO) measure, as adapted for use in a
      population of adults with moderate to severe hemophilia A treated with coagulation factor
      VIII (FVIII) therapy as secondary prophylaxis or episodic treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
