  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Male, 18 to 50 years of age

          -  Diagnosis of moderate to severe hemophilia A (documented &lt;1-2% Factor VIII
             Concentration [FVIII:C])

          -  Willing to maintain current FVIII treatment regimen, whether prophylactic or
             on-demand, for the duration of the study

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Routine need for wheelchair or routine need for two canes or crutches

          -  Diagnosis of another bleeding disorder such as von Willebrand Disease

          -  Known event that would interfere with the scheduled CAJAS evaluations (e.g., elective
             joint surgery, vacation)
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
